name: It's a Quacky Zoo!
description:
Baby animals are the snuggliest! This super patterned quilt has pink and white stripes on one side and an array of squares filled with polka dots, plaid, elephants, monkeys, giraffes and more playful little baby animals all over the other side.

The quacky quilts listed are:
Machine washable and dry-able
Warm and cuddly
One-of-a-kind, no two are alike
Note: quilts are not flame-retardant
36 x 42 inches

Perfect for tummy time on the floor!

These baby quilts are great for photos. 

Nothing makes your sweet baby's smile stand out like the lovely patterns and colors of a Quack Quack Quilt!

Word on the street is puppies and kittens love them too;)

Remember, since these are one-of-kind they'll be gone soon! Buy yours now!!
